------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project includes a clean-room Go port of the Quack wire codec
originally written in Java for `com.gizmodata:quack-jdbc`
(https://github.com/gizmodata/quack-jdbc, MIT). Both projects ultimately
trace the wire format documentation to
`https://github.com/tobilg/quack-protocol` by Tobi (MIT).

The driver is built on the Apache Arrow ADBC Go framework
(https://github.com/apache/arrow-adbc, Apache-2.0) and the Apache Arrow Go
library (https://github.com/apache/arrow-go, Apache-2.0); both ship under
their own license terms, which apply to those libraries.
